






                                                 TestML Usage Overview

     * Software to Test
       * In some language
       * (Preexisting test framework)
     * TestML Framework
       * TestML Compiler
     * Test Suite
       * .tml files
       * Simple Assertions
       * Large Body of Data
     * TestML Bridge class
       * In software's language
     * The `testml` CLI
       * Or `prove`, etc









